
#### 4. tools/aztec-tools.md
**Description**: A file listing useful tools for Aztec Network development.

**Sample Content**:
```markdown
# Tools for Aztec Network Development

This file lists tools and utilities for building on the Aztec Network.

- **Aztec CLI**: Command-line interface for starting the sandbox, deploying contracts, and interacting with the network.
  - Install: `npm install -g @aztec/cli`
- **Noir VS Code Extension**: Syntax highlighting and snippets for Noir.
  - Install from VS Code Marketplace.
- **Aztec Test Runner**: GitHub Action for running transaction execution tests in CI.
  - See [AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec](https://github.com/AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec)[](https://github.com/AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec)
- **Remix IDE Plugin**: Plugin for compiling and deploying Aztec contracts in Remix IDE.
  - Available in Remix Plugin Marketplace.

For more tools, check the [awesome-aztec repository](https://github.com/AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec).

---
Source: [AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec](https://github.com/AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec)[](https://github.com/AztecProtocol/awesome-aztec)
